        args='{"prompt": "In {{spacex_s1}}, retrieve any risk factor disclosures related to controlled-company status, concentrated voting control by Elon Musk, and the reduced governance protections for Class A shareholders. Include any text about the ability of Class B stockholders to elect 51% of the board and the implications for board independence and minority shareholder protections."}',
